    rdau:P61101 "<a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Xiao_Hong'>Wikipedia</a>, katsottu 6.9.2024 (Xiao Hong: Xiao Hong or Hsiao Hung (1 June 1911 – 22 January 1942) was a Chinese writer. Her infant name (乳名，ruming) was Zhang Ronghua (張榮華). Her formal name used at school (學名，xueming) was Zhang Xiuhuan (張秀環). Her name Zhang Naiying (張廼瑩) was changed by her grandfather; she also used the pen names Qiao Yin and Lingling.)"@fi ;
